          <h2 style="font-size:24px;line-height:1.2;font-weight:500;">
        Childhood vaccination drop </h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
         <p style="font-size:18px;line-height:1.5;">
         <strong>
      Summary: The vaccination percentage drops due to economic inequality, misinformation, and aid cuts. </strong>
         </p>
          <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;">
       Global <a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #06266D; color: black;" href="https://link.geopoliticalsummary.com/gs-26-jun-25-spotlight-h2-4-childhood-vaccination-efforts" target="_blank">childhood vaccination efforts</a> are faltering due to economic inequality, pandemic-related disruptions, and the rise of misinformation. Since 1974, immunization programs have saved about 154Mn lives. However, there has been a notable slowdown since the 2010s. 
          </p>
          <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;">
         Measles vaccinations are down by half in half of all countries. The pandemic disrupted routine vaccinations, leaving nearly 13Mn children unvaccinated between 2020 and 2023. In 2023, over half of the world's 15.7Mn unvaccinated children lived in just eight countries, mostly in sub-Saharan Africa.</p>
          <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;">
        Vaccine misinformation, political instability, economic inequality, and <a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #06266D; color: black;" href="https://link.geopoliticalsummary.com/gs-26-jun-25-spotlight-h2-5-foreign-aid-cuts" target="_blank">foreign aid cuts</a> have made the situation worse. Outbreaks of measles and polio are returning, hitting areas like the US, the EU, Pakistan, and Papua New Guinea. </p>
        <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;">
        Researchers warn these setbacks jeopardize the WHO’s 2030 vaccination goals. Recently, Bill Gates described the situation in Africa as a “tragedy” and <a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #06266D; color: black;" href="https://link.geopoliticalsummary.com/gs-26-jun-25-spotlight-h2-6-pledged-1-6b" target="_blank">pledged $1.6B</a> to the Gavi vaccine alliance to support ongoing immunization efforts.</p>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
